redeclipse (1.2-3) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * Add unversion lib dependency alternatives
    - libgl1-mesa-dev | libgl-dev
    - libsdl1.2-dev | libsdl-dev
    - lib1g-dev | libz-dev
  * Enable hardening build flags
    - dh compat level 9
    - Added build-with-ldflags.patch:
      Patch which appends $(LDFLAGS) to all end-targets
    - Removed build-with-debug-symbols.patch:
      Now handled in d/rules instead
  * Enable parallel build

 -- Martin Erik Werner <martinerikwerner@gmail.com>  Mon, 27 Feb 2012 13:53:19 +0100

